## Essentials

` { doc: "A null value. To export as `null` in JSON or ~ in YAML."
    export: :suppress }
null: __NULL

` { doc: "`cons(h, t)` - construct new list by prepending item `h` to list `t`."
    example: cons(0,[1,2]) //=> [0,1,2]
    export: :suppress }
cons: __CONS

` { doc: "`head(l)` - return the head item of list `l`, error if empty."
    export: :suppress }
head: __HEAD

