    export: :suppress }
elements: __ELEMENTS

` { doc: "`block(l)` - (re)construct block from list `l` of elements."
    export: :suppress }
block: __BLOCK

` { doc: "`has(s, b)` - true if and only if block `b` has key (symbol) `s`."
    export: :suppress }
has(s, b): TODO(__HAS(b, s))

` { doc: "`lookup(s, b)` - look up symbol `s` in block `b`, error if not found."
